      "content": "I would not recommend skipping your basal dose tonight, even if you didn't eat much for dinner. Skipping a dose can throw off your insulin balance and lead to unpredictable blood sugar fluctuations. Instead, you can adjust your carb count for the evening by adding more snacks or adjusting your dinner portion size for the next day. If you're still concerned, consider consulting with your healthcare provider or a registered dietitian for personalized guidance.",
