      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but i'm just really worried about a low overnight. my blood sugar is already pretty low right now since i barely ate. wouldn't it be safer for me to just skip it this one time instead of risking a hypoglycemic episode while i'm asleep? it seems more logical to just skip a dose if there's no food to process.",
